text: Samuel Groth and Chris Guccione were the defending champions, but they did not participate this year. Li Zhe and Jose Rubin Statham won the tournament, defeating Dean O'Brien and Ruan Roelofse in the final, 6–4, 6–2. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==External links== * Main Draw Gimcheon Open ATP Challenger - Doubles 2015 Doubles
